dct_title_s: Chart showing the positions and comparisons of the observations in and across the Gulf Stream, in 1845-46-47 & 48
dct_description_sm: Shows coast from Cape Lookout, N.C. to Cape Cod, Mass. In upper margin: Plate No. 2. Engraved for Blunt's, Memoir, of the Atlantic Ocean, 1851. Plate no. 2 includes illustrations of Saxton's metallic thermometer. From: Notes on the Gulf Stream, by A.D. Bache, in: Memoir of the dangers and ice in the North Atlantic Ocean / [compiled by G.W. Blunt]. New-York : E. & G.W. Blunt, 1852.
